  <div class="row-12-col">
    <div class="card white-text">
      <div class="card_title">
        <h2>Alona Blue Sailing Charters</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="card_body bordered">
        <p>
          Welcome aboard Alona Blue, we invite you to come and join us for an unforgettable experience sailing,
          and exploring the magnificent aqua blue waters around Panglao and Bohol Islands in the Philippines.
        </p>

        <p>
          Magical snorkeling fabulous food and drinks, good music, personal service - it's all possible on our beautiful
          new 36' sailing catamaran, Alona Blue.
        </p>

        <p>
          We offer a relaxed and personalized yacht charter service to ensure you take away a truly memorable
          experience.
        </p>

        <p>Take a moment to view our web site to see photos and the trips we offer.</p>

        <p>We look forward to hearing from you and answering any questions you may have.</p>

        <p>
          Please visit
          <a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/g1066348-d7276083" target="_blank">Alona Blue on TripAdvisor</a> for
          reviews by our quests. We are #1 in Activities in Tagbilaran City!
        </p>

        <p>Hope to see you soon,</p>

        <p>Fair Winds,</p>

        <p>Capt Mike, Jenny, and Foxy</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card_support">
        <%= render 'book_now_btn' %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
